    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《弹射牛仔》——快节奏的多人乱斗游戏，子弹四处反弹，每个人都为自己而战，乱斗一触即发。《弹射牛仔》目前不支持中文版本。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>混乱的对决</strong> </h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《弹射牛仔》中，所有的子弹、爆炸和互动都基于物理效果，使混乱成倍增加，也为竞技技巧打开了大门。在这个子弹会反弹、一击致命的游戏中，你也很有可能击中自己。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/4afc8e9c99595d0551ea9fbe5ee5e71e.poster.avif?t=1731406700\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/4afc8e9c99595d0551ea9fbe5ee5e71e.webm?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/4afc8e9c99595d0551ea9fbe5ee5e71e.mp4?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/3ce09012d3a482e3351cb8a632b46478.avif?t=1731406700\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tools of the West</strong></h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >躲避反弹子弹只是战斗的一部分——你需要利用所有可用工具来生存和取胜。匕首是你在装填子弹间歇期内称霸近战的最佳选择，如果你反应足够快，甚至可以挡住子弹，但再快的匕首也挡不住一根好时机的炸药棒。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/cf04d1139d19ff6e6621743f68039c89.poster.avif?t=1731406700\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/cf04d1139d19ff6e6621743f68039c89.webm?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/cf04d1139d19ff6e6621743f68039c89.mp4?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/3ce09012d3a482e3351cb8a632b46478.avif?t=1731406700\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>沙发多人模式 &amp; 在线对战</strong> </h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最多可有8个好友加入同一个沙发上战斗，或者在Steam上一起加入每一轮的混战。在每一轮的3分钟内，争取尽可能多的击杀数！</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/ec5ad1993ade6c0adf671ae442dfb093.poster.avif?t=1731406700\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/ec5ad1993ade6c0adf671ae442dfb093.webm?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/ec5ad1993ade6c0adf671ae442dfb093.mp4?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/3ce09012d3a482e3351cb8a632b46478.avif?t=1731406700\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>像素化的西部世界</strong> </h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏以经典的意大利西部电影风格和滚滚尘土为背景，呈现像素化的低分辨率视觉效果，伴随弹道轨迹和飞溅的碎片。</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/7a1a17b7f84e3275b0c165a6152ee184.poster.avif?t=1731406700\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/7a1a17b7f84e3275b0c165a6152ee184.webm?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/7a1a17b7f84e3275b0c165a6152ee184.mp4?t=1731406700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167380/extras/3ce09012d3a482e3351cb8a632b46478.avif?t=1731406700\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>竞技精通</strong> </h2> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你沉浸在混战中，反弹角度将成为你的朋友。利用角度制造更多混乱，翻桌子挡子弹，并掌握在空中击落炸药的技能，成为乱斗中的高手！</p> <p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
